---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="eCommerce.cat - Agència eCommerce a Catalunya">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
          Desenvolupament eCommerce Professional
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mb-8">
        Creem experiències<br />
        <span class="text-[#55C7DC]">eCommerce</span> úniques<br />
        i rentables
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
        Transformem la teva visió en una botiga online que <strong class="font-semibold">vén i fidelitza</strong>. 
        Com agència eCommerce especialitzada, desenvolupem plataformes que s'integren completament en els teus processos.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center mb-16">
        <a 
          href="#contacte" 
          class="px-10 py-5 bg-white text-[#1B5585] font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-white/50 hover:scale-105 inline-flex items-center gap-3"
        >
          Demana una consulta
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#serveis" 
          class="px-10 py-5 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-white/30 hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1B5585] hover:scale-105"
        >
          Descobreix els serveis
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">50+</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-light">Projectes completats</div>
        </div>
        <div class="backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">10+</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-light">Anys d'experiència</div>
        </div>
        <div class="backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">5</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-light">Plataformes dominades</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proposta de Valor -->
  <section id="proposta" class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <span class="inline-block px-6 py-2 mb-6 text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase rounded-full bg-[#55C7DC]/10 text-[#1B5585]">
          LA NOSTRA PROPOSTA
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#1B5585]">
          Per què eComm360?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          En el mercat digital actual, una botiga online estàndard no és suficient. El teu negoci necessita una plataforma que satisfaci les expectatives dels teus clients i potenciï les teves vendes.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#55C7DC] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1B5585]">Solucions a Mesura</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Adaptades als teus processos específics, sense plantilles genèriques.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#55C7DC] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1B5585]">Experiència Multiplataforma</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            T'oferim la solució que millor s'adapti al teu negoci.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#55C7DC] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1B5585]">Enfocament en Conversió</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Cada decisió es pren per incrementar les teves vendes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#55C7DC] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1B5585]">Escalabilitat</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Plataformes preparades per créixer amb tu.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#55C7DC] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1B5585]">Integració Nativa</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Connectem amb ERP i sistemes d'automatització des del principi.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Final -->
  <section id="contacte" class="py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1B5585] to-[#55C7DC] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Parlem del teu projecte
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Estàs a punt per llançar la teva nova botiga online o portar el teu eCommerce al següent nivell?
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="mailto:info@ecomm360.es" 
          class="px-10 py-5 bg-white text-[#1B5585] font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl hover:scale-105"
        >
          info@ecomm360.es
        </a>
        <a 
          href="tel:+34933903137" 
          class="px-10 py-5 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-white/30 hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1B5585]"
        >
          (+34) 933 903 137
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-12 text-lg">
        <strong>eComm360</strong><br />
        Pla. Urquinaona, 6, 14B<br />
        08010, Barcelona, España
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
